Package: transdoc
Title: Translate Text, Web, and Help documents
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Atsushi",
           family = "Yasumoto",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "atusy.rpkg@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8335-495X"))
Description: Translate text, web, and help documents to a specified language.
  Especially, the replaced `?` function would be useful for non-native English
  users. In the ".Rprofile" file, add `option(transdoc_to = "your-language")`
  such as `"ja"` for Japanese to change the default destination language.
URL: https://transdoc.atusy.net/, https://github.com/atusy/transdoc
BugReports: https://github.com/atusy/transdoc/issues
